<section>
<p style="Heading 1">Page Numbers Dialog</p>
<p style="Normal"><c style="Normal">This dialog inserts page numbers on every page of your document.</c><c style="Normal"></c></p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c style="Heading 2">Position</c><c style="Heading 2"></c></p>
<p style="Normal">Click on the appropriate radio button to put the page numbers in the header or footer of your document.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c style="Heading 2">Alignment</c><c style="Heading 2"></c></p>
<p style="Normal">Click on the appropriate radio button to put the page numbers at the left, center, or right of the header or footer.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c style="Heading 2">Preview</c><c style="Heading 2"></c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c style="Normal">This display shows the selected position of the page number relative to the main text of the page.</c><c style="Normal"></c></p>
<p style="Heading 2">Help</p>
<p style="Normal"><c style="Normal">This button </c>opens the documentation for this dialog<c style="Normal">.</c><c style="Normal"></c></p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c style="Heading 2">Cancel</c><c style="Heading 2"></c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c style="Normal">This button closes the dialog without inserting the page numbers.</c><c style="Normal"></c></p>
<p style="Heading 2">Insert</p>
<p style="Normal">This button inserts the page numbers and closes the dialog.</p>
</section>
